data.description: This stunning Park Ridge residence boasts an inviting open floor plan that's perfect for modern living. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, 42-inch wood cabinets, and a spacious island that's ideal for meal preparation and casual dining. Most recent upgrades include a new roof equipped with solar panels for energy efficiency. In addition, newer windows and doors for improved insulation, and an abundance of recessed lighting that adds to the bright and welcoming atmosphere. The main level of the house comprises a spacious living room and dining area, offering an ideal setting for family gatherings and entertaining. Additionally, there is a convenient first-floor bedroom that can easily serve as a home office, providing flexibility to accommodate various lifestyle needs. The lower level of the home features a generously sized family room, perfect for both playtime and entertaining guests. There is also a bonus "4 season" room that comes equipped with storms and screens, a window air conditioner, and a gas space heater, offering a versatile space for various purposes. The property boasts an oversized, heated, and insulated 2.5-car garage, providing ample space for vehicles and additional storage needs. Ideal location, close to great schools, major transportation arteries such as the "blue line", I90 and 294, as well as shopping and restaurants. Welcome Home!
